branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
Series CVJ3 is a valve mounted cylinder with single acting, spring return or spring extend actuation. The CVJ3 is available in a 10mm or 16mm bore with 3 mounting options. A cylinder with the auto switch installed can also be manufactured.
&lt;/p&gt;

